Runops-Movie version 0.01
=========================

To make a movie:

  perl -MRunops::Movie=run your-program 2> movie.log
  frame-runner < movie.log
  ffmpeg -i frame-%05d.png movie.mp4


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  blah blah blah

